{"tid":575135,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"中國飛機片《紅海行動》香港上映成為「三級片」","createTime":"2018-02-28T04:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T08:46:57.000Z","uid":41343,"like":8,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f8caed62ef155248ebdb97ce1004da8b44d5be06","tid":575135,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T04:28:17.000Z","msg":"電影《紅海行動》自上映以來，票房和口碑持續走高，日前票房已經突破22億。據香港媒體報導，《紅海行動》將於3月1日在香港上映，且全片138分鐘將一刀未剪悉數上映，並被定級為「三級片」上映。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，《紅海行動》中有不少展現戰爭殘酷的場景，其中不乏一些斷肢殘骸、血肉模糊等血腥場景，故而根據香港電影的分級原則，將被定為「三級片」上映，而被分級為「三級片」的電影在播放正片前也會有相關提示，明確未成年人不得觀看，影院可保留追究責任的權利。此前，《死侍》、《神探》、《人肉叉燒包》、《古惑仔》等多部香港電影也均因血腥場面而在香港被定為三級。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/122752_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F122752_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e8debbfa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6fb6ed8546334538b3b15ca6da816c3b974b567","tid":575135,"uid":57604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T04:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248b4658b25221399f43acb2aeeee3bf93e74583","tid":575135,"uid":11962,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T04:29:36.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲飛機片"},{"pid":"2fbf05b582090755b1164d9c08a7ec37ef109f84","tid":575135,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T04:30:21.000Z","msg":"唔撚係啊, 雷霆救兵點解又唔三級啊 ???"},{"pid":"e94f9b3541c09086eecd26bd2b76a34bb0b52e06","tid":575135,"uid":23635,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T04:30:35.000Z","msg":"咁樣咪包唔到場俾學生睇囉？"},{"pid":"4b39bd39a1331610a4435e8a61cc69d6c0e03516","tid":575135,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e94f9b3541c09086eecd26bd2b76a34bb0b52e06","tid":575135,"uid":23635,"like":